# UI Components Rules

## Permitted Paths (Write Access)
- `src/components/**` — all shared visual layout units

## Approved Reference Paths (Read-Only)
- `src/store/**` (to read data hook interfaces)
- `src/data/widgetTemplates.json`

## Restricted Paths
- All files in `src/engine/**`
- All files in `src/pages/**`
- All files in `src/store/**` (direct state mutations inside component files are forbidden)

## Presentation Layer Guidelines
- Shared components should avoid inline store updates. Trigger Zustand actions instead.
- Use `React.memo` for rendering canvas nodes that update frequently.
- Utilize standard CSS transitions for smooth micro-animations. Avoid adding third-party transition libraries.
- Render Konva widgets strictly within Konva Stage/Layer structures.
- Apply clipping path masks for round frames visually in the preview canvas (DeviceFrame overlay).
